SeedStack Business framework

Packages 
Package Description
org.seedstack.business.api
Provides general APIs of the Business Framework.
org.seedstack.business.api.domain
Provides classes for the domain layer.
org.seedstack.business.api.domain.events
Contains all the domain events provided by the framework.
org.seedstack.business.api.domain.identity
Contains classes related to the entity identity creation.
org.seedstack.business.api.domain.stereotypes
Contains annotations representing intents.
org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces
Provides classes for the interface layer.
org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces.assembler
Contains all the classes related to the assembly pattern.
org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces.assembler.dsl
Provides classes specific to the assembler DSL.
org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces.finder
Provides classes for CQRS-style queries.
org.seedstack.business.api.interfaces.view
Provides classes for representing view concepts like chunk or page.
org.seedstack.business.jpa
Provides infrastructure classes specific to JPA.
org.seedstack.business.spi
Provides all the classes available to extend the API.
org.seedstack.business.test
Provides classes for testing business objects.
org.seedstack.business.test.event
Provides classes for testing events.
